title: The Memeology Religion
author: blockhead1110
pages:
#-  The Memology Religion§0
§0
§0                 by§0
§0        blockhead1110§0
§0
§0A fascinating look and in-depth interview with a devoted follower of one of 3.0's many bizarre religions.
#- Special thanks to Der_Wunderbus, for instructing me in the ways of the Memeology religion. 
